{"title":"string","uid":"5c8a0474d0d497359d76757037b0b5f8","slug":"string","date":"2023-08-01T07:06:37.000Z","updated":"2023-08-02T15:17:00.343Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/string.json","keywords":"serverDream's blog","cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"String\"><a href=\"#String\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"String\"></a>String</h1><h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义\"></a>定义</h2><p>C++的string标准库string是C++标准库的重要部分，主要用于字符串处理。</p>\n<h2 id=\"操作\"><a href=\"#操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作\"></a>操作</h2><h3 id=\"导入头文件\"><a href=\"#导入头文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"导入头文件\"></a><strong>导入头文件</strong></h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;cstring></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"定义-1\"><a href=\"#定义-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义\"></a><strong>定义</strong></h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">string <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>字符串名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"赋值\"><a href=\"#赋值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"赋值\"></a><strong>赋值</strong></h3><p>赋值为<strong>字符串</strong>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>字符串名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;字符串>\"</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>赋值为<strong>string</strong>变量</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>字符串名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>字符串名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"在末尾添加字符或字符串\"><a href=\"#在末尾添加字符或字符串\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在末尾添加字符或字符串\"></a><strong>在末尾添加字符或字符串</strong></h3><p>添加为<strong>字符串</strong>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>字符串名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;字符串>\"</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>添加<strong>string</strong>变量</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>字符串名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>字符串名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"查看字符串大小\"><a href=\"#查看字符串大小\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看字符串大小\"></a><strong>查看字符串大小</strong></h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>字符串名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"访问字符串中的某个字符\"><a href=\"#访问字符串中的某个字符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"访问字符串中的某个字符\"></a><strong>访问字符串中的某个字符</strong></h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-langua